parameters.customQuery:
SELECT 
 addr.SystemId, 
 addr.ParentId, 
 addr.CMMContainer, 
 addr.Id, 
 addr.AddrTypeCd, 
 addr.Addr1, 
 addr.Addr2, 
 addr.Addr3, 
 addr.Addr4, 
 addr.City, 
 addr.StateProvCd, 
 addr.PostalCode, 
 addr.County, 
 addr.RegionCd, 
 addr.RegionISOCd, 
 addr.PreDirectional, 
 addr.PrimaryNumber, 
 addr.StreetName, 
 addr.Suffix, 
 addr.PostDirectional, 
 addr.SecondaryDesignator, 
 addr.SecondaryNumber, 
 addr.VerificationMsg, 
 addr.VerificationHash, 
 addr.Latitude, 
 addr.Longitude, 
 addr.Score, 
 addr.PrimaryNumberSuffix, 
 addr.DPV, 
 addr.DPVDesc, 
 addr.DPVNotes, 
 addr.DPVNotesDesc, 
 addr.Attention, 
 addr.BarcodeDigits, 
 addr.CarrierRoute, 
 addr.CongressCode, 
 addr.CountyCode, 
 addr.AdditionalLegal, 
 addr.Section, 
 addr.Township, 
 addr.Lot, 
 addr.Range, 
 addr.Addition, 
 addr.Block, 
 addr.LegalDesc, 
 addr.TownshipDir, 
 addr.RangeDir, 
 addr.Validated, 
 addr.PrimaryMeridian, 
 addr.PLSSCounty, 
 addr.AddressHash, 
 addr.GeocodeLevel, 
 addr.GeocodeLevelDescription, 
 addr.Meridian, 
 addr.AddressOverrideInd, 
 addr.DistanceToCoast, 
 addr.DistanceToCoastInd, 
 addr.AddrAliasModifiedInd, 
 addr.Country,
 addr.RowId
 FROM addr addr 
INNER JOIN advrxxchangedbeans b
   ON addr.Systemid=b.Systemid
  AND addr.CmmContainer=b.CmmContainer
  AND b.CmmContainer = 'Application'
WHERE concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' 
  AND concat(adddt,addtm)<='$$m_Enddt'
  AND (   AddrTypeCd LIKE '%Mailing%'
       OR AddrTypeCd LIKE '%Risk%'
       OR AddrTypeCd LIKE '%CoverageStreetAddr%')
